OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FA day of sunny spells and
OL,6,Fshowers, with the most frequent and
OL,7,Fheaviest showers towards the north of
OL,8,Fthe region. Temperatures remaining a
OL,9,Flittle below average.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,12,FFurther sunshine and showers
OL,13,Fthroughout Wednesday before a spell of
OL,14,Fwet and windy weather moves in for
OL,15,FThursday. A return to showers on
OL,16,FFriday, but perhaps turning drier
OL,17,Flater.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
